column4: As a user I need a registration page to create and account
As a user, I want a home and maps page so I can easily navigate the website
As a user I want to find rock climbing and hiking locations
As a user I want to input locations and dates so I can search for rides
As a user I want to be able to chat with other users
As a user, I want to be able to favorite locations that I most enjoy.
As a user, I want to see information about  travelers similar to me so I can choose a ride
As an user, I should be able to rate the driver or rider
As a driver I want post my destination and costs
As a user I want to find a ride to [destination]
As a user I want to be able to edit my profile and add information about myself
As a user, I want to add attributes about myself so I can interact with others most similar to me.
As a user, I want to navigate to the registration page so I can start entering my info
As a user I want to browse possible destinations or interesting locations on the map
As a user I want to view all my messages
As a user I want to be able to search for users to chat
As a user I want to add fun spots on the map or view existing spots
